    public abstract class GraphicsAlgorithmImpl
extends GraphicsAlgorithmContainerImpl
implements GraphicsAlgorithm
    An implementation of the model object 'Graphics Algorithm'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Background
    • Foreground
    • Line Width
    • Line Style
    • Filled
    • Line Visible
    • Rendering Style
    • Transparency
    • Graphics Algorithm Children
    • Parent Graphics Algorithm
    • Pictogram Element
    • Width
    • Height
    • X
    • Y
    • Style
